<bibRefCitation id="10885FC6F1158444FD9DB9B866908002" author="Mozaffarian, Fariba" journalOrPublisher="Zootaxa" pageId="0" pageNumber="83231" pagination="475 - 501" refId="B7712977" refString="Mozaffarian, Fariba, 2018. An Identification key to the species of Auchenorrhyncha of Iranian fauna recorded as pests in orchards and a review on the pest status of the species. Zootaxa 4420 (4): 475 - 501" title="An Identification key to the species of Auchenorrhyncha of Iranian fauna recorded as pests in orchards and a review on the pest status of the species" volume="4420" year="2018">Mozaffarian 2018</bibRefCitation>
